"profileDescription.element.dominant.earth" = "Earth dominance adds practicality, sensuality, and patience. You trust what is stable and tangible.";
"profileDescription.element.dominant.fire" = "Fire dominance adds impulse, confidence, and expressive force. You are drawn to choices that feel alive.";
"profileDescription.element.dominant.water" = "Water dominance adds intuition, empathy, and emotional depth. You respond strongly to atmosphere.";
