"profileDescription.moon.aquarius" = "You need emotional space and intellectual honesty. Too much pressure can make you detach.";
"profileDescription.moon.aries" = "Emotionally, you need directness and quick release. Waiting too long can feel heavier than acting.";
"profileDescription.moon.cancer" = "You need tenderness, privacy, and a trusted emotional home before you fully open up.";
"profileDescription.moon.capricorn" = "You feel safest when things are reliable, responsible, and not overly chaotic.";
"profileDescription.moon.gemini" = "You process feelings by naming them, discussing them, and moving between perspectives.";
"profileDescription.moon.leo" = "Your feelings are warm and proud. Recognition, affection, and sincere attention help you recharge.";
"profileDescription.moon.libra" = "Your emotional balance depends on peace, fairness, and a beautiful atmosphere around you.";
"profileDescription.moon.pisces" = "Your emotional world is empathic and fluid. Music, images, quiet, and softness restore you.";
"profileDescription.moon.sagittarius" = "Your mood improves with movement, honesty, humor, and a sense that life is still opening.";
"profileDescription.moon.scorpio" = "You feel deeply and privately. Trust matters more than speed, and emotional truth is essential.";
"profileDescription.moon.taurus" = "Your emotional body calms down through stability, touch, routine, and familiar pleasures.";
"profileDescription.moon.virgo" = "You regulate emotions through order, usefulness, and small improvements that make life cleaner.";
